description:
http://IRockJazz.com IRockJazz caught Roy Hargrove in Chicago, and he discusses the importance of music in his life, his roots, and inspiration for his music.  In this clip, Roy says it isn't about having a job or making money, you have to put more into it then that, and if you do, the music will take care of you.

Interested seeing more great interviews? Visit www.irockjazz.com
